{
  "stem": "26465.2",
  "chunk_idx": 7,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And we were sitting next to them, and the next thing I know, my-- my friend, Helen, wanted to go to the washroom.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So in that crowd, in that terribly stuffy-- but where do we go to the washroom?",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] we were having such difficulties.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "We finally got there, and when we got there, we couldn't go back to the couple anymore-- it was so packed, and there was some-- some problem there.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "The people wanted to jump through the windows or something, because the-- start-- the-- the Germans started shooting.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we were so scared, so we pushed ourselves against the wall, and we just sat there on the floor.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And we didn't see anything-- the night was dark.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "We didn't know where we were going and what we were doing.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We were very scared-- two scared girls.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When we arrived in Krakow, we were driven-- or rather escorted-- on foot to someplace, I believe there was this-- I have no idea what place was it.",
      "word_count": 28
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because I've never seen that big of city.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[DRINKS] And anyway, there was a huge courtyard, and people were formed in quadrangle on all four sides.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And in the middle there were policemen and the dogs-- it was sort of between snow and rain, very, very wet time, somewhere around 12:00, maybe 1:00, past midnight.",
      "word_count": 29
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In December.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We were very scared and very cold.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And we didn't know what to-- what to expect.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "People were being-- next to us, for example, there was this lady who started shrieking.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "She got-- she was pregnant--",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "She was pregnant, and she started bleeding-- she had probably, what's it called?",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Was aborting.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 23,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And-- this-- this old man came out to-- to ask a gestapo if there could be something done for her.",
      "word_count": 20
    }
  ],
